name: angry
trans: Feeling mad or upset about something.

name: bridge
trans: A structure built over water or a road so people can cross.

name: chapter
trans: One part or section of a book.

name: climb
trans: To go up something like a tree, ladder, or hill.

name: delicious
trans: Tasting very good; yummy.

name: enough
trans: As much as you need; not too little.

name: finish
trans: To complete something; to reach the end.

name: guess
trans: To try to answer without knowing for sure.

name: healthy
trans: In good health; strong and well.

name: insect
trans: A small creature with six legs, like a bee or ant.

name: joke
trans: Something funny you say or do to make people laugh.

name: known
trans: Something that people have information about; familiar.

name: listen
trans: To pay attention to sounds or what someone is saying.

name: minute
trans: A short period of time; sixty seconds.

name: neighbor
trans: A person who lives near you.

name: outside
trans: Not inside a building; in the open air.

name: party
trans: A fun gathering of people to celebrate something.

name: question
trans: Something you ask when you want to know information.

name: reach
trans: To stretch out your arm to touch or get something.

name: second
trans: Coming after the first; also a very short unit of time.

name: special
trans: Different from others in a good way; important.

name: tiny
trans: Very, very small.

name: understand
trans: To know what something means.

name: valley
trans: Low land between hills or mountains.

name: wonder
trans: To think about something or want to know about it.

name: yesterday
trans: The day before today.

name: accept
trans: To agree to take or receive something.

name: balloon
trans: A rubber bag filled with air or gas that floats.

name: choose
trans: To pick one thing from several options.

name: discover
trans: To find something for the first time.

name: eleven
trans: The number 11.

name: forest
trans: A large area with many trees growing close together.

name: grow
trans: To get bigger or taller over time.

name: honest
trans: Telling the truth; not lying.

name: invite
trans: To ask someone to come to an event or place.

name: journey
trans: A trip from one place to another.

name: knock
trans: To hit a door or surface to make a sound.

name: leave
trans: To go away from a place.

name: middle
trans: The center point or part that is between two sides.

name: nearby
trans: Close; not far away.

name: office
trans: A room or building where people work at desks.

name: present
trans: A gift; also means here or now.

name: remember
trans: To think of something again; not to forget.

name: shout
trans: To speak or call out very loudly.

name: station
trans: A place where trains or buses stop to let people on and off.

name: together
trans: With each other; in the same place.

name: usual
trans: Normal; what happens most of the time.

name: vacation
trans: Time away from school or work for fun and rest.

name: watch
trans: To look at something; also something you wear on your wrist that tells time.

name: youngster
trans: A young person; a child or young boy or girl.

name: against
trans: Touching or pushing on something; opposed to.

name: beach
trans: Sandy land next to the ocean or a lake.

name: clothes
trans: Things you wear on your body like shirts, pants, and dresses.

name: dragon
trans: A large imaginary creature in stories that breathes fire.

name: engine
trans: A machine that makes things move, like in a car or train.

name: fire
trans: The hot, bright flames that burn things.

name: grandmother
trans: The mother of your mother or father; your grandma.

name: hurry
trans: To move or do something quickly.

name: idea
trans: A thought or plan in your mind.

name: jumped
trans: Pushed yourself off the ground with your legs (past tense of jump).

name: kitchen
trans: The room where food is cooked.

name: lesson
trans: A period of time when you learn something at school.

name: magic
trans: Special powers that can make impossible things happen.

name: north
trans: The direction toward the top of a map; opposite of south.

name: openly
trans: In a way that is not hidden; honestly.

name: pencil
trans: A tool for writing or drawing that has a wooden case and graphite center.

name: quietly
trans: In a way that makes little or no noise.

name: rock
trans: A hard piece of stone.

name: shape
trans: The form or outline of something, like a circle or square.

name: third
trans: Coming after the second; number 3 in order.

name: toward
trans: In the direction of; moving closer to something.

name: until
trans: Up to the time when something happens.

name: village
trans: A small town in the country with houses and shops.

name: while
trans: During the time that something is happening.

name: xylophone
trans: A musical instrument with bars that you hit with small hammers to make sounds.

name: yourself
trans: You; your own self.

name: after
trans: Coming later in time or following something.

name: bright
trans: Giving off a lot of light; shining.

name: collect
trans: To gather things together from different places.

name: draw
trans: To make a picture with a pencil, crayon, or pen.

name: energy
trans: The strength and power to do things and stay active.

name: finish
trans: To complete something; to reach the end.

name: greatest
trans: The most great; the best or biggest of all.

name: holiday
trans: A special day when people don't work or go to school to celebrate.

name: inside
trans: In or into a building or container; not outside.

name: jungle
trans: A thick forest in a hot place with many plants and wild animals.

name: kindly
trans: In a nice and caring way.

name: lamp
trans: A light that you can turn on and off.

name: market
trans: A place where people buy and sell food and other things.

name: never
trans: Not ever; at no time.

name: order
trans: To arrange things in a certain way; also to ask for something.

name: problem
trans: Something that is difficult or needs to be solved.

name: quickly
trans: In a fast way; doing something with speed.

name: ride
trans: To sit on and travel in or on something like a bike or car.

name: silent
trans: Making no sound at all; completely quiet.

name: taller
trans: Having more height than something else.

name: understood
trans: Knew what something meant (past tense of understand).

name: voice
trans: The sound you make when you speak or sing.

name: weekend
trans: Saturday and Sunday; the days when most people don't work or go to school.

name: zoo
trans: A place where wild animals are kept for people to see.
